{
  "stem": "13063.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every group had a-- every group had to belong to a working place, you see?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And thus, from the ghetto, we were marched to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Pole-- the-- the Poles were-- were looking at us, staring, and enjoying the sight of Jews being-- being marched, you know, like-- like prisoners of war, or worse, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to the camp at Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were just staring and enjoying the sight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] In Plaszow, it was already a different story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You-- you remember from the movie, there was Amon Goeth, the commandant of the Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a killer, a real killer, a sadistic killer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He killed for pleasure, for his own personal pleasure.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at that time, I saw people being killed in the-- in the-- in-- in the camp for not saying that what he was doing is right and accepted by them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he used to go and he asked a group of people, who doesn't like here what I-- what I am doing in this camp, shooting people?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who doesn't like it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So nobody answered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ah, I see you don't like it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Out-- shot him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Ah, you don't seem to like my actions, my deportment, my behavior.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Come out-- boom.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the people saw what's going on, so started crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Jews, have-- have mercy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Say something here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So everybody starts, oh, we are very happy what you are doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You are-- you are a-- you are a great man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We are-- you're very-- you are doing the right thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This put him to-- to rest, in other words, that this-- this stilled his rabid feelings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "What did he look like?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
